items.Video_Title: How to style black in summer. Capsule Wardrobe.
items.Video_Description:
Hello my Lovely People

This video is for those of you who love wearing black regardless of the temperatures outside.

Why do we love black?
Black is slimming.
Black is chic and edgy.
Black adds personality.

Don’t disregard black only because it doesn’t suit you, you can always wear it as an addition in a form of stripes, accessories or bottoms like shorts or skirt. 

Black adds a little contrast or a frame to your outfit, something I often do when I feel my look is too predictable.

Thank you so much for watching, subscribing to my channel and for your lovely comments😊
